@greet(name) → message
  You receive a name. Say hello to them warmly.
  Your output is just the greeting message.
  ? message contains name
  ? message is one sentence

@wrap(greet.message) → text, emoji
  You receive a greeting message.
  Pass it through as text, and pick a fitting emoji.
  ? text is the original message unchanged
  ? emoji is exactly one emoji character
